  "body": "When running deposit simulation in `mode = \"simulation\"` with input file `inputFile = \"validator_test_data.json\"` the following `java.lang.ArithmeticException: / by zero` error is thrown when in method `get_beacon_proposer_index`.\r\n\r\nIn our current implementation `v0.7.1` debugging is difficult (4 min wait time). We are waiting until after changes are made to how our `DepositContract` is deployed to begin debugging.\r\n\r\n```\r\n> Task :run\r\nSetting logging level to INFO\r\n10:40:58.948 [INFO ] - ******* Eth2Genesis Event detected ******* : 0xD56342AFD67EC47A07545D73D78F1A545D6E294BE7A4BF3D34BF23319355CC80\r\n10:40:58.948 [INFO ] - Node slot: 0\r\n10:40:58.948 [INFO ] - Node time: 0\r\n10:41:00.022 [INFO ] - Initial state root is 0xAA48CB73258733B18CCC90E565074C3D3B8958312CD4346EA441D3CF2BCB8588\r\n10:41:00.022 [INFO ] - Genesis block root is 0x010E77C10B6AD09B59ED1D47A8B6DEC78F93C7B342FE10FEA0BD41B23A7A6ADD\r\nJul 10, 2019 10:41:00 AM com.google.common.eventbus.EventBus$LoggingHandler handleException\r\nSEVERE: Exception thrown by subscriber method onGenesisHeadStateEvent(tech.pegasys.artemis.statetransition.GenesisHeadStateEvent) on subscriber tech.pegasys.artemis.validator.coordinator.ValidatorCoordinator@3ffb3598 when dispatching event: tech.pegasys.artemis.statetransition.GenesisHeadStateEvent@1f137bcd\r\njava.lang.ArithmeticException: / by zero\r\n\tat com.google.common.primitives.UnsignedLongs.remainder(UnsignedLongs.java:294)\r\n\tat com.google.common.primitives.UnsignedLong.mod(UnsignedLong.java:171)\r\n\tat tech.pegasys.artemis.datastructures.util.BeaconStateUtil.get_beacon_proposer_index(BeaconStateUtil.java:592)\r\n\tat tech.pegasys.artemis.validator.coordinator.ValidatorCoordinator.createBlockIfNecessary(ValidatorCoordinator.java:403)\r\n\tat tech.pegasys.artemis.validator.coordinator.ValidatorCoordinator.onNewHeadStateEvent(ValidatorCoordinator.java:258)\r\n\tat tech.pegasys.artemis.validator.coordinator.ValidatorCoordinator.onGenesisHeadStateEvent(ValidatorCoordinator.java:187)\r\n\tat java.base/jdk.internal.reflect.NativeMethodAccessorImpl.invoke0(Native Method)\r\n\tat java.base/jdk.internal.reflect.NativeMethodAccessorImpl.invoke(NativeMethodAccessorImpl.java:62)\r\n\tat java.base/jdk.internal.reflect.DelegatingMethodAccessorImpl.invoke(DelegatingMethodAccessorImpl.java:43)\r\n\tat java.base/java.lang.reflect.Method.invoke(Method.java:566)\r\n\tat com.google.common.eventbus.Subscriber.invokeSubscriberMethod(Subscriber.java:87)\r\n\tat com.google.common.eventbus.Subscriber$SynchronizedSubscriber.invokeSubscriberMethod(Subscriber.java:144)\r\n\tat com.google.common.eventbus.Subscriber$1.run(Subscriber.java:72)\r\n\tat java.base/java.util.concurrent.ThreadPoolExecutor.runWorker(ThreadPoolExecutor.java:1128)\r\n\tat java.base/java.util.concurrent.ThreadPoolExecutor$Worker.run(ThreadPoolExecutor.java:628)\r\n\tat java.base/java.lang.Thread.run(Thread.java:834)\r\n\r\n\r\n> Task :run FAILED\r\n```\r\n\r\n`config.toml`\r\n```\r\n[deposit]\r\n# normal, test, simulation\r\n# \"test\" pre-production\r\n# \"simulation\" to run a simulation of deposits with ganache-cli, if a inputFile is included the file will replay the deposits\r\n# \"normal\" production, must include contractAddr and nodeUrl\r\nmode = \"simulation\"\r\ninputFile = \"validator_test_data.json\"\r\nnumValidators = 16\r\nnumNodes = 1\r\ncontractAddr = \"0x77f7bED277449F51505a4C54550B074030d989bC\"\r\nnodeUrl = \"http://localhost:7545\"\r\n```",
